/* Description */
A plugin for adding site search powerd by Yahoo!'s BOSS

/* Instructions */
   1. Download the plugin and put it in /app/plugins/yahoo_boss.
   2. Get an API key from yahoo (http://developer.yahoo.com/wsregapp/).
   3. Rename /app/yahoo_boss/config/yahoo_boss.php.default to /app/yahoo_boss/config/yahoo_boss.php
   4. Update /app/yahoo_boss/config/yahoo_boss.php with site and api key
   5. Access the search from http://yourapp/yahoo_boss/search
   6. Optionally add a route if you prefer to use a different URL.
      For example: Router::connect('/search/:term/*', array('controller' => 'search', 'action' => 'results'));


